  int SEQ_LENGTH = 5;
  int SUB_LENGTH = 3;

  generateSubsequences(sequence, SEQ_LENGTH, SUB_LENGTH);
}
```

This code creates a loop that iterates through the sequence and extracts all contiguous subsequences of the specified length. Since we're taking contiguous subsequences, there's no possibility of duplicate elements with different orders.

